4. ALFWorld
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Shridhar et al., Microsoft Research. License: MIT.
   Embodied household agent benchmark. An MIT LICENSE text matching the upstream
   ALFWorld terms (reconstructed; see the note at the top of the file) is included
   under third_party/verl-agent/.../env_package/alfworld/alfworld/.

   GPL component (disclosure): the vendored ALFWorld copy also includes the
   Metric-FF planner (Joerg Hoffmann) under
   .../alfworld/alfworld/gen/ff_planner/, whose C sources carry GNU General Public
   License v2-or-later headers. It is a standalone game-generation tool: it is NOT
   compiled, linked, or imported by FedAgent's Apache-2.0 code, and is NOT used by
   the released WebShop/ALFWorld experiments (which run on pre-generated game files
   fetched via download_data.sh). It is shipped only as mere aggregation; its GPL
   terms apply solely to that subdirectory, per the headers in its source files.

