6. Bundled data derived from WebShop / ALFWorld
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   data/env_heterogeneity/ ships small data files derived from the WebShop and
   ALFWorld benchmark data (items 3-4 above, both MIT):
   - lookalike_data/*.json and holdout_webshop_v1.json, synthesized from WebShop's
     items_shuffle_1000.json / items_ins_v2_1000.json product data.
   - holdout_alfworld_v1.json, derived from the ALFWorld game data.
   These derived files are distributed under the same MIT terms as their source
   benchmark data, whose LICENSE texts are preserved in the vendored copies under
   third_party/verl-agent/.../env_package/{webshop,alfworld}/.
